{"tid":363842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔會放棄香港","createTime":"2017-08-18T02:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T04:45:09.000Z","uid":12633,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e26292b876c619cedc3c68c73a425c9a528a76","tid":363842,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"作為一個廢青，<br />\n至少，<br />\n我唔要成為冷漠無腦既港豬；<br />\n我唔會成為扼搾年輕人既廢老；<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人生本來就毫無意義，<br />\n我又有何包袱可言？<br />\n<br />\n至多，<br />\n絕望之為虛妄，正與希望相同；<br />\n既然做、同唔做，最後結果都可能係一樣；<br />\n我會係愚公，<br />\n我會係西西弗斯，<br />\n我會係卡繆，<br />\n我會係魯迅，<br />\n我會係歷史上寂寂無名既抗爭者，<br />\n我會係出師未捷埋百土既無名氏，<br />\n<br />\n我會係我 &mdash;<br />\n臨死之前，<br />\n我唔會比自己後悔，<br />\n我唔要比自己羞愧，<br />\n人生毫無意義，但幸好我生存過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只要呢度仲有一個真正既香港人，呢度就係值得我奮鬥既地方。"},{"pid":"513fa8df7b06b54a90ae5ae2e580f8cf91a9bd51","tid":363842,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11608622c7cac937a28e6d773b45f2c640ff61d9","tid":363842,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港放棄你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算連登放棄肥絲老師，我都唔會放棄你"},{"pid":"1a6ce80c01f37cd45f8d3adda9b7d77d9f7b54eb","tid":363842,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:25:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f271c22b94f319a3b50981f8ad582a0dc73ab15","tid":363842,"uid":61994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"佔中個時都好多人似你咁熱血<br />\n<br />\n我都相信你同好多真正香港人一樣，得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bee9738b2ccbe91e89f2711b60feb8fd60115f","tid":363842,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港放棄你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就算連登放棄肥絲老師，我都唔會放棄你</blockquote><br />\nI have a boyfriend.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI go to school by bus"},{"pid":"e1e527787e13075a894b86217b8318c82159579f","tid":363842,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佔中個時都好多人似你咁熱血<br />\n<br />\n我都相信你同好多真正香港人一樣，得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比起你既相信我，我更相信我自己"},{"pid":"204e952b1cbe15f9faf836eea923b8c68678bc11","tid":363842,"uid":130230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"不如你講下實質你想做啲乜好過啦, 成日喺度鳩叫做乜？"},{"pid":"fc227ecfca49cc3cd385221ffa39b4fd250d8235","tid":363842,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如你講下實質你想做啲乜好過啦, 成日喺度鳩叫做乜？</blockquote><br />\n係連登鳩up本身已經影響緊好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54575dd5bd74e8c0d1390a9905d7d6ce9d680234","tid":363842,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如你講下實質你想做啲乜好過啦, 成日喺度鳩叫做乜？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信念，<br />\n念念不忘，必有，唔知咩野發生。"},{"pid":"1ad77e3e46f0478349f68e58ff22ff66e8eaf237","tid":363842,"uid":72205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"好！"}]}